    <p>I am an associate professor in the department&nbsp;<a href="https://iitbhilai.ac.in/index.php?pid=dept_cse">EECS</a>
      at <a target="_blank" data-cke-saved-href="https://www.iitbhilai.ac.in/index.php"
        href="https://www.iitbhilai.ac.in/index.php" class="navigation_external_link">IIT
        Bhilai.</a> Earlier, I worked as an assistant professor of CSE at IIT
      Gandhinagar (2014-17). I obtained my BE, MTech and PhD degrees from
      Jadavpur University (1994 - 98), Indian Statistical Institute (1999 - 01)
      and KU Leuven (2001 - 06), respectively. I spent a long span of time
      (about 8 years) working as a postdoctoral (or guest) researcher at various
      places in Europe, USA, and Canada, namely, KU Leuven (2006 - 08), NIST,
      USA (2008 - 12) and University of Waterloo (2012 - 14).</p>
    <p>Since 2001, my research has always centered on cryptography and related
